#. Translators: The title of the Enhanced Clipboard Reading settings panel.
#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:20 buildVars.py:21
msgid "Enhanced Clipboard Reading"
msgstr "Poboljšano čitanje privremene memorije"

#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:26
msgid "&Maximum clipboard length before using browsable message (characters):"
msgstr ""
"&Maksimalna dužina privremene memorije pre nego što se koristi poruka režima "
"pretraživanja (u znakovima):"

#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:49
msgid ""
"Reports the text on the Windows clipboard. Pressing twice spells this "
"information. Pressing three times displays the clipboard contents in a "
"browsable window. If the clipboard exceeds the configured character limit, a "
"browsable window is shown on the first press, and additional presses are "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"Prijavljuje tekst u Windows privremenoj memoriji. Pritiskanje dva puta sriče "
"ovu informaciju. Pritiskanje tri puta će prikazati informaciju u poruci "
"režima pretraživanja. Ako privremena memorija sadrži više teksta od "
"podešenog ograničenja znakova, poruka režima pretraživanja će biti prikazana "
"nakon prvog pritiskanja, a dodatna pritiskanja će biti zanemarena."

#. Translators: Presented when there is no text on the clipboard.
#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:65
msgid "There is no text on the clipboard"
msgstr "Nema teksta u privremenoj memoriji"

#. Translators: Title of the browsable message showing clipboard contents.
#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:79
#: addon\globalPlugins\enhancedClipboardReading.py:87
msgid "Clipboard contents"
msgstr "Sadržaj privremene memorije"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
msgid ""
"Enhances the default NVDA+C command to read the clipboard with a "
"configurable character limit instead of the hardcoded value of no more than "
"1023. If there is more text on the clipboard than the configured limit, "
"presents the clipboard text in a browseable message for easier reviewing, "
"instead of saying that the clipboard contains a large portion of text. A "
"browseable message can also be opened at any time by pressing NVDA+C three "
"times quickly, even if there is less text on the clipboard than the "
"configured limit."
msgstr ""
"Poboljšava podrazumevanu NVDA komandu NVDA+C za čitanje privremene memorije "
"ograničenjem znakova koje se može podesiti umesto unapred definisane "
"vrednosti koja ne može biti veća od 1023. Ako privremena memorija sadrži "
"više teksta od podešenog ograničenja, prikazuje poruku u režimu "
"pretraživanja radi lakšeg pregleda, umesto da izgovori da privremena "
"memorija sadrži velik deo teksta. Poruka režima pretraživanja se takođe može "
"otvoriti u bilo kom trenutku pritiskanjem NVDA+C brzo tri puta, čak i ako "
"ima manje teksta u privremenoj memoriji od podešenog ograničenja."

